<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/about.css">

</head>
<body class="p-8 md:p-12">

    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="text-center py-6 mb-8 border-b-2 border-dashed" style="border-color: var(--border-color);">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold" style="color: var(--text-color);">About Our Company</h1>
    </header>

    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav class="flex justify-center mb-12">
        <ul class="flex space-x-6 text-lg" style="color: var(--text-light);">
            <li><a href="feed" class="hover:underline">Home</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <!-- Main Content Section -->
    <main class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Aside (Sidebar) -->
        <aside class="lg:col-span-1 p-6 bg-gray-800 card" style="background-color: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
<p class="text-base leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-light);">
    Our mission is to connect people through shared passions and hobbies. Whether you're into painting, gaming, photography, or gardening, our platform offers a space where enthusiasts can collaborate, learn, and grow together. We believe that hobbies build community, spark creativity, and enrich lives.
</p>
        </aside>

        <!-- Main Section with multi-column text -->
        <section class="lg:col-span-2 p-6 bg-gray-800 card" style="background-color: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-6">Our Story</h2>
<p class="multi-column-text text-base text-justify leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-light);">
    Our journey began with a simple idea: create a digital space where people can meet others who share their interests. In a world dominated by fast-paced social media, we wanted to build a calmer, more meaningful experience: a place where conversations revolve around hobbies and personal growth.
    <br><br>
    Since launching, our hobby social site has grown into a vibrant community of creators, learners, and doers. From virtual book clubs and art challenges to DIY tutorials and niche forums, we provide the tools and connections to help you explore what you love and meet like-minded people around the world.
</p>
        </section>
    </main>
    
    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="text-center py-6 mt-12 text-sm" style="color: var(--text-light);">
        <p>&copy; 2024 Your Company. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
